OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCharities warn fuel poverty
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcould double in a year     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The number of fuel poor households in  
OL,6, the UK will double in a year if the    
OL,7, crisis in Ukraine leads to higher      
OL,8, energy bills, charities are warning.   
OL,10,FAnalysts are predicting that the war   
OL,11,Fhas pushed up wholesale prices, and    
OL,12,Fcould mean the average domestic bill in
OL,13,Fthe UK hits #3,000 in October.         
OL,15,FNational Energy Action said that would 
OL,16,Fput 8.5 million households in serious  
OL,17,Ffinancial difficulty from fuel bills.  
OL,19,FThat would be twice the number of a    
OL,20,Fyear earlier, equating to 30% of homes.
